{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Metaball Force"], "type": "title", "extent": [35, 54], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [54, 101], "text": ["Applies forces according to metaballs."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [101, 327], "text": ["This tool applies a force to particles according to how close they are to metaballs. It puts down a ", {"text": ["POP Metaball Force"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popmetaballforce", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/dop/popmetaballforce"}, " in the DOP network, and also a ", {"text": ["Force SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/force", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/force"}, " in the SOP network."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [366, 476], "text": ["Create some metaballs using the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/metaball", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "SOP/metaball"}, {"text": ["Metaball"], "fullpath": "/shelf/metaball", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/metaball"}, " shelf tool."]}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [476, 656], "text": ["Create a particle system using the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/POP/location", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "POP/location"}, {"text": ["Location"], "fullpath": "/shelf/dynamics_poplocation", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/dynamics_poplocation"}, " or ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/POP/source", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "POP/source"}, {"text": ["Source"], "fullpath": "/shelf/dynamics_popsource", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/dynamics_popsource"}, " shelf tools."]}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [656, 775], "text": ["Click the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/force", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "SOP/force"}, {"text": ["Metaball Force"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popmetaballforce", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/dop/popmetaballforce"}, " tool on the ", {"text": ["Particles"], "type": "ui"}, " tab."]}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [775, 887], "text": ["Select the metaballs you want to affect your ", {"text": ["particles"], "fullpath": "/dopparticles/index", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/dopparticles/"}, " and press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, "."]}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [887, 1123], "text": ["You can set the ", {"text": ["Force Scale"], "type": "ui"}, " parameter on the ", {"text": ["Metaball Force"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popmetaballforce", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/dop/popmetaballforce"}, " node to either attract or repel particles. A positive value will attract particles and a negative value will repel particles. "]}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1123, 1347], "text": ["By default, this tool applies a ", {"text": ["Radial Force"], "type": "ui"}, ", which can be changed to ", {"text": ["Directional Force"], "type": "ui"}, " on the ", {"text": ["Force SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/force", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/force"}, ". There are also force controls for axial, vortex, and spiral forces."]}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1347, 1431], "text": ["The following example shows the metaballs repelling the particles."]}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1431, 1494], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/images/shelf/POPmetaball.png", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "/images/shelf/POPmetaball.png"}]}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Using Metaball Force"], "extent": [327, 366], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": "includeme"}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [1494, 1602], "text": ["For specific parameter help, see the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/force", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "SOP/force"}, {"text": ["Metaball Force"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popmetaballforce", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/dop/popmetaballforce"}, " node help."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1611, 1656], "text": [{"text": ["Location"], "fullpath": "/shelf/dynamics_poplocation", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/dynamics_poplocation"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1656, 1696], "text": [{"text": ["Source"], "fullpath": "/shelf/dynamics_popsource", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/dynamics_popsource"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "extent": [1602, 1611], "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "summary": ["Applies forces according to metaballs."], "type": "root", "attrs": {"tags": "particles", "icon": "SOP/force"}, "title": ["Metaball Force"]}